[Civil No. 1033. Filed January 14, 1908.] TOMASA FRANK, Administratrix of the Estate of ABE FRANK, Deceased, Appellant, v. THE SOUTHERN PACIFIC RAILROAD COMPANY OF ARIZONA, and THE SOUTHERN PACIFIC RAILROAD COMPANY, Appellees. APPEAL from a judgment of the District Court of the First Judicial District, in and for the County of Yuma. John H. Campbell, Judge. "Wupperman & Wupperman, for Appellant. Prank Cox and Alfred Franklin, for Appellees.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted. ,
